Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.09,0:00:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I knew it would turn out like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.51,0:00:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have taken the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.44,0:00:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't like it from the start...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.37,0:00:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is going to be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.20,0:00:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.58,0:00:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's just a scratch!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.00,0:00:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost at the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, no hospitals.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.67,0:00:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said a doctor, but not a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.09,0:00:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Hellblau Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.68,0:00:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I know what you're trying to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.64,0:00:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go to a hospital, the police will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.26,0:00:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then you'll be back in prison again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.18,0:01:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.48,0:01:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time to get to that\Nunderground doctor's place!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.23,0:01:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the Hellblau Hotel...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.77,0:01:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your life is more important!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.11,0:01:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you're alive, you can...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.48,0:01:10.03,Default 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.03,0:01:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Hellblau Hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.46,0:01:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.87,0:01:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,nothing good ever comes from\Ngetting involved with women.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.00,0:01:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.92,0:01:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,get to Dr. Tenma quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.46,0:03:06.31,Location,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(185,0)\pos(362,307)}Two Months Ago
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.73,0:03:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behave yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.73,0:03:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person you're about to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:11.88,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(280,200)\pos(362,343)}An Unpleasant job
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.44,0:03:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is someone you wouldn't be able\Nto see under normal circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.90,0:03:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I should've brought my autograph book.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.03,0:03:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you if you joke around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.58,0:03:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.97,0:03:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This man, Martin, is my subordinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.97,0:03:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.89,0:03:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish to speak with him alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.06,0:03:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll really kill you if you screw something up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.12,0:04:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I sit here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.22,0:04:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long have you been with The Baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.52,0:04:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost three years, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.31,0:04:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And before that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prison, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.45,0:04:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many years?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.78,0:04:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eight years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.95,0:04:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.12,0:04:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.16,0:04:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got out rather quickly, considering.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.16,0:04:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was an exemplary inmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.67,0:04:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you're exemplary when it\N\Ncomes to doing jobs, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.21,0:04:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.84,0:04:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.76,0:04:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Except...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Except?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.14,0:05:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not too thrilled with jobs that involve women.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.51,0:05:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I won't be picky about my jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't want to get involved with women.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.90,0:05:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This job does involve a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.31,0:05:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to look after a certain woman for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.53,0:05:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An unpleasant job...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.58,0:05:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to pick up a certain woman from D{\fnMeiryo U}ü{\fnNarkisim}sseldorf.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.46,0:05:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you say you don't like to get involved with women...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.46,0:05:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you should be perfect for this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.17,0:05:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be able to keep things professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.48,0:05:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Eva Heinemann?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.44,0:05:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:05:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Martin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.32,0:06:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't think my name matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.86,0:06:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was told to take you to Frankfurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.03,0:06:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Told by whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.95,0:06:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man wearing glasses and an expensive suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man wearing glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.33,0:06:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not with Roberto's group, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.66,0:06:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know much myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he seems to be a very important person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to go, I won't force you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.96,0:06:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not too thrilled about this, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.35,0:06:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being targeted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.02,0:06:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be my bodyguard?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.43,0:06:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's part of my job, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.03,0:06:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carry this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.57,0:06:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.58,0:06:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better than getting killed by that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.21,0:06:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an unpleasant bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.79,0:06:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way she shakes her ass...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.75,0:07:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The smell of her perfume...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It pisses me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.55,0:07:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.02,0:07:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you talk to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we can talk about something if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.11,0:07:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really feel like talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.99,0:07:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any drinks?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.00,0:07:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't there any drinks?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I don't drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go check the dining car.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.53,0:08:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So you're traveling alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.11,0:08:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm traveling alone myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.87,0:08:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, if you don't mind, could you please\Ntell me where you'll be staying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here. This is my card.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.46,0:08:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This woman asked me for a drink, so I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.34,0:08:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you lay a finger on this woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.46,0:09:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you talk while you're eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.47,0:09:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, I'll talk if you want me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.14,0:09:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you drink alcohol?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mom was a terrible alcoholic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.06,0:09:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't mind if you drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.77,0:09:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother probably had a reason why she had to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.74,0:09:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a reason I have to drink...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.03,0:09:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, please, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.54,0:09:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is, if you don't like eating without a conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.21,0:09:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a long story.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.67,0:09:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.63,0:09:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to have a fianc{\fnMeiryo U}é{\fnNarkisim}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a Japanese surgeon...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.27,0:10:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with brilliant skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I tried to kill my former fianc{\fnMeiryo U}é{\fnNarkisim}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, are you surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.95,0:10:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to kill that man!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.96,0:10:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you didn't shoot him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.13,0:10:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your story is better than mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.51,0:10:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your story?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.76,0:10:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... actually pulled the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.14,0:10:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My girlfriend was on top of some guy in the bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.52,0:10:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shot the guy along with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.52,0:10:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,until the gun ran out of bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.36,0:10:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The room was filled with the smell of\Nher blood, the smell of his blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:10:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the smell of her perfume...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:10:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I realized it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.58,0:11:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was standing alone in the middle of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.88,0:11:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.26,0:12:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an unpleasant job...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.44,0:12:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My employer is waiting at this hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.87,0:12:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you killed someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.58,0:12:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.38,0:12:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which room?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.63,0:12:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way you're dressed isn't suited for this hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.97,0:12:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.51,0:12:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's room 1014.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.57,0:12:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.49,0:13:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what the man with the glasses will say to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.71,0:13:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if that woman refuses his deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.92,0:13:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this unpleasant job will be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.42,0:13:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't have to deal with that woman anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.39,0:13:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't look too good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.31,0:13:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a bad deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.65,0:13:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said I could use this card as much as I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.41,0:13:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.62,0:13:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.37,0:13:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we going
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.62,0:13:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.38,0:13:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really hate this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.26,0:14:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place next.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.84,0:14:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they sell men's suits here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.84,0:14:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need you to look decent, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.18,0:14:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.18,0:14:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.35,0:14:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't have a man in my company looking so shabby.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.48,0:14:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.98,0:14:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for the necktie...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.37,0:15:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenzou...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.57,0:15:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try this on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.92,0:15:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Necktie, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.38,0:15:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hideous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.43,0:15:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.26,0:15:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.27,0:15:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look a little better.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.73,0:15:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.81,0:15:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wear your tie properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.99,0:15:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop walking around with your shoulders\Nslouched like a gangster.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.16,0:15:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was walking normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.41,0:15:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your "normal" isn't normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.29,0:15:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, you have to guard me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.05,0:16:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure I won't be embarrassed.\Nno matter where I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.97,0:16:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's your job, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.81,0:16:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.15,0:16:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't put your elbow on the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.32,0:16:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fork in your left hand, knife in your right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.61,0:16:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make any noises when you're eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.49,0:16:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.41,0:16:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.58,0:16:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your story.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.58,0:16:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That you were the daughter of\Nthe director of a big hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.50,0:16:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You thought it was a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.34,0:16:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I brought you to this city...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.34,0:16:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you just seemed like an alcoholic woman,\Nno matter how I looked at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.38,0:16:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm quite different now, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.59,0:16:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look like a classy lady, no two ways about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my true form.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.39,0:16:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eva Heinemann just returned to where she belongs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.52,0:17:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.98,0:17:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An invitation to a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.74,0:17:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A party?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.57,0:17:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.49,0:17:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was the Job that was given to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.99,0:17:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Job?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.37,0:17:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To attend several parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.29,0:17:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.25,0:17:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.54,0:17:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like a fun job.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.29,0:17:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're coming as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.29,0:17:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be my escort, a gentleman worthy of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.63,0:17:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is getting more unpleasant by the second.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.41,0:18:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How does it feel to finally be back on home ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.24,0:18:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are all these people talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.66,0:18:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The weather?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.08,0:18:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stocks?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.95,0:18:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even tell what language they're speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.63,0:18:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to feel sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.56,0:18:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.56,0:19:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.18,0:19:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.44,0:19:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.44,0:19:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.11,0:19:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.90,0:19:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't at this party.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.15,0:19:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My job here is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.61,0:19:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who wasn't here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.41,0:19:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me away from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.74,0:19:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care where!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.04,0:19:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hurry up and take me away from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.75,0:19:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.92,0:19:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know why this woman's hand was trembling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.73,0:19:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've managed to somehow survive the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.94,0:19:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.73,0:19:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you return to the place where you belong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.70,0:19:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My life used to be like that every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.74,0:20:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought if I returned to that world...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.25,0:20:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the real me would come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.13,0:20:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.46,0:20:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,places like this bar are the only places\Nwhere you feel comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.38,0:20:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't belong in a place like this, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.76,0:20:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.88,0:20:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not places like that, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.01,0:20:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no place for me, no matter where I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.31,0:20:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.02,0:20:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that after I've finished this job...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.07,0:20:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll surely be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.41,0:20:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it'd be better than staying a mess and\Ngetting killed by Roberto in D{\fnMeiryo U}ü{\fnNarkisim}sseldorf.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.75,0:20:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it'd be better to die as the\Nwell-dressed Eva Heinemann.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.67,0:20:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's all the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.30,0:20:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once I'm dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.89,0:21:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.65,0:21:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My bad habit came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.99,0:21:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the time, I suddenly thought to myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.61,0:21:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I wanted to protect this woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.52,0:21:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.69,0:21:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How the hell did this happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.27,0:21:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's why I'm going to tell...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.28,0:21:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everything to Dr. Tenma right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.95,0:22:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.57,0:22:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.37,0:22:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.58,0:22:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Necktie...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.71,0:22:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I didn't have something like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.46,0:22:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have had to go to a place like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.09,0:22:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have had to...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.59,0:22:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,see something so terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.84,0:22:31.01,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(170,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.01,0:22:44.44,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,475)}Cherish what you know is true in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.01,0:22:44.44,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(201,21)}Ima kono sekai de wakaru koto mitsumete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.44,0:22:47.40,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(182,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.40,0:23:01.08,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(198,472)}Please believe in the kindness of your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.40,0:23:01.08,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,21)}Anata no hitomi no yasashisa wo shinjite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.68,0:23:25.94,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(196,473)}Make it home to your land of harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.94,0:23:34.36,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(195,473)}Make it home to your land of purity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.36,0:23:36.82,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,246)\pos(187,472)}Make it home
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.97,0:23:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
